## Scantailor Advanced

* Scantailor-advanced -> https://github.com/4lex4/scantailor-advanced

Instalar:

    cd /opt/src
    git clone https://github.com/4lex4/scantailor-advanced.git scantailor-advanced
    cd scantailor-advanced
    cmake .
    make
    make install # o checkinstall


#### Cmake

`scantailor-advanced` requiere una version de `cmake` que no está en `Ubuntu 16.04`, para compilar instalar una version mas reciente:

Descargar la última version estable desde <https://cmake.org/download/>, ejemplo:


    cd /opt/src
    wget https://cmake.org/files/v3.12/cmake-3.12.4.tar.gz
    tar xzvf cmake-3.12.4.tar.gz
    cd cmake-3.12.4
    
luego compilar:

    ./bootstrap
    make -j4
    sudo make install

(en vez de `make install` puede utilizarse `checkinstall`)    
para saber si se instalo correctamente:
    
    cmake --version

mas info en [How do I install the latest version of cmake from the command line?](https://askubuntu.com/questions/355565/how-do-i-install-the-latest-version-of-cmake-from-the-command-line)

#### Libboost

Remover version del sistema:

    sudo apt-get --purge remove libboost-dev && sudo apt-get --purge remove libboost-all-dev && sudo apt-get --purge autoremove libboost-all-dev

Descargar la version necesaria desde http://www.boost.org/, luego: 

    tar -xzvf boost_1_XX_X.tar.gz
    cd boost_1_XX_X
    ./bootstrap.sh
    ./b2

ver mas en: [Install Boost 1.64 in Ubuntu 16.04](https://tnonline.wordpress.com/2017/07/12/install-boost-1-63-in-ubuntu-16-04/), [Find correct Boost version installed and how to remove the old version](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/47627874/find-correct-boost-version-installed-and-how-to-remove-the-old-version) [ Installing Boost 1.64 on Ubuntu 16.04 won't install Boost above 1.58](https://ubuntuforums.org/showthread.php?t=2363177)

para instalar:

    sudo ./b2 install
    # o bien 
    sudo checkinstall ./b2 install 

* <https://scaron.info/blog/cmake-can-use-a-local-boost.html>
